# Input
```svelte
<!-- should generate diagnostics -->

<!-- Static alt text with redundant words is flagged in Svelte files -->
<img alt="Photo of friend." />
<img alt="Image of cool person" aria-hidden="false" />
<!-- Redundant word in the static portion of a template value -->
<img alt="image of {person}" />
<img alt="photo by {photographer}" />
<img alt="picture: {description}" />

```

# Diagnostics
```
invalid.svelte:4:10 lint/a11y/noRedundantAlt ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

  × Avoid the words "image", "picture", or "photo" in img element alt text.
  
    3 │ <!-- Static alt text with redundant words is flagged in Svelte files -->
  > 4 │ <img alt="Photo of friend." />
      │          ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
    5 │ <img alt="Image of cool person" aria-hidden="false" />
    6 │ <!-- Redundant word in the static portion of a template value -->
  
  i Screen readers announce img elements as "images", so it is not necessary to redeclare this in alternative text.
  

```

